{"tid":242963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩想同自己個母親大人講?","createTime":"2017-05-14T10:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T10:59:33.000Z","uid":91082,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe04fc1feacb39caf431326591fae908f4a5d53","tid":242963,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"多謝你咁多年嚟嘅照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你病嘅時候，我仲用咁差嘅態度對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又發你脾氣，又嫌你煩，成日駁嘴<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到而家冇咗先嚟後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人永遠都係失去先嚟後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位要珍惜眼前人。<br />\n不過我都明白好多嘢都係心中，<br />\n好難講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n唔講出口唯有用行動表達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母親節快樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc29bf051c222036630fc63e575d184328d6697","tid":242963,"uid":108176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"雖然你係我一歲既時候已經離開左我同爸爸 但多謝你賜予我生命。媽 母親節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535afdf5f673c0507d461435c64dd5fa64cfc688","tid":242963,"uid":59705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"母親節先黎扮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}